He was a good guy.

00:26:14.528 --> 00:26:18.720
And the people loved him and worked very hard to please him and make the kingdom great.

00:26:18.816 --> 00:26:28.864
one day the king of this prospering kingdom wanted to show his gratitude to the people who loved and served him so the king sent out an invitation to all the people of this

00:26:28.384 --> 00:26:30.880
full of the land to join him at his palace.

00:26:30.560 --> 00:26:40.608
And once everyone arrived, the king began to have his servants bring valued treasures and other possessions from his palace out into the great courtyard in front of the king's palace.

00:26:40.128 --> 00:26:40.928
I don't know.

